1
00:01:01,920 --> 00:01:02,399
Hey

2
00:01:02,880 --> 00:01:04,280
Look at the time already

3
00:01:04,280 --> 00:01:05,439
Why aren't they here yet?

4
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:08,599
Reporting, Your Highness

5
00:01:08,599 --> 00:01:09,560
Report

6
00:01:10,799 --> 00:01:12,120
Where is my vanguard army?

7
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:13,079
Why haven't they arrived?

8
00:01:13,120 --> 00:01:15,280
The vanguard ran into bandits on the way

9
00:01:15,439 --> 00:01:16,920
These bandits are extremely fierce

10
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:18,719
The vanguard is currently engaged in battle

11
00:01:18,959 --> 00:01:19,799
Estimated

12
00:01:19,799 --> 00:01:21,239
they'll be delayed by three days.

13
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:23,439
Useless fools!

14
00:01:23,519 --> 00:01:24,799
What kind of bandits?

15
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:26,120
Three days and three nights?

16
00:01:26,799 --> 00:01:27,799
Get the hell out, all of you!

17
00:01:27,959 --> 00:01:28,760
Yes, sir

18
00:01:30,519 --> 00:01:32,200
Who knew such a mishap would happen?

19
00:01:32,319 --> 00:01:33,159
Then we...

20
00:01:33,599 --> 00:01:35,799
We'll just stay a few more days

21
00:01:35,799 --> 00:01:36,319
Mm

22
00:01:46,319 --> 00:01:49,439
Maybe I'll dress as my father again and try.

23
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:50,599
It won't work.

24
00:01:50,799 --> 00:01:51,560
Any trick we've used before

25
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:53,000
won't work anymore.

26
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:54,480
If you ask me,

27
00:01:54,599 --> 00:01:56,120
let's just grab him first

28
00:01:56,319 --> 00:01:57,760
and beat him up.

29
00:01:58,519 --> 00:01:59,640
Are you stupid?

30
00:01:59,719 --> 00:02:01,319
You can't beat him in his own dream.

31
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:03,680
But he just refuses to leave.

32
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:04,519
Don't tell me

33
00:02:04,519 --> 00:02:06,640
we have to keep dreaming along with him forever?

34
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:09,560
Let me think it over.

35
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:11,919
What are you all thinking about?

36
00:02:15,919 --> 00:02:18,319
Are you worried about the vanguard army,

37
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,159
or

38
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:21,159
is something else going on?

39
00:02:22,319 --> 00:02:23,400
Would you like me

40
00:02:23,639 --> 00:02:25,400
to help you figure it out?

41
00:02:25,879 --> 00:02:26,680
Uh...

42
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:28,319
Imperial Uncle.

43
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:30,919
We were just...

44
00:02:31,639 --> 00:02:33,360
What kind of secret

45
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:35,080
are you three young people sharing?

46
00:02:35,319 --> 00:02:37,840
Why not share it with me too?

47
00:02:39,080 --> 00:02:39,879
Let's give it a try.

48
00:02:40,439 --> 00:02:41,400
There's actually another way.

49
00:02:41,479 --> 00:02:42,280
Ah!

50
00:02:43,919 --> 00:02:45,039
Are you crazy?

51
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,879
Why are you tying me up?

52
00:02:47,199 --> 00:02:48,919
You little princess of Yan,

53
00:02:49,039 --> 00:02:50,479
how can you be so rude?

54
00:02:52,039 --> 00:02:53,479
Listen, Imperial Uncle Liu.

55
00:02:54,039 --> 00:02:55,240
You know full well

56
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,680
why I'm hitting you, don't you?

57
00:02:57,319 --> 00:02:58,120
Hmph.

58
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,080
What did you say?

59
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:02,120
I have no idea what you're talking about.

60
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,080
Imperial Uncle Liu,

61
00:03:03,199 --> 00:03:04,479
hurry up and let us go.

62
00:03:04,759 --> 00:03:05,319
What you're doing

63
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:06,479
is so disappointing.

64
00:03:07,439 --> 00:03:08,400
Imperial Uncle Liu,

65
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:09,520
let's get straight to the point.

66
00:03:09,719 --> 00:03:12,080
We already know we're inside your dream.

67
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:13,360
If you don't want to send troops,

68
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,439
we'll find another way.

69
00:03:14,439 --> 00:03:16,599
Please stop trapping us in your dream.

70
00:03:16,719 --> 00:03:17,360
Hmm.

71
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,520
What nonsense.

72
00:03:20,439 --> 00:03:21,919
What dream are you talking about?

73
00:03:23,199 --> 00:03:24,719
I swore last night

74
00:03:25,319 --> 00:03:26,800
I'd never touch that

75
00:03:27,479 --> 00:03:28,319
Dream Wanderer Wine again.

76
00:03:28,919 --> 00:03:30,919
What dream?

77
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:32,319
Imperial Uncle Liu,

78
00:03:32,439 --> 00:03:33,919
you're still lying to us.

79
00:03:33,919 --> 00:03:34,919
Last night,

80
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:37,080
both of them saw you with that Yue'er.

81
00:03:37,719 --> 00:03:38,840
If that's not a dream, what is it?

82
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:40,080
You're still trying to deny it?

83
00:03:40,919 --> 00:03:41,759
Oh.

84
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:43,479
Hey.

85
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,080
Last night,

86
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:48,080
I think I did have a dream.

87
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:50,919
I dreamed I was playing chess with Yu'er.

88
00:03:52,319 --> 00:03:53,360
What are you doing?

89
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:55,240
Knock him out.

90
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,439
He won't tell the truth anyway.

91
00:03:57,439 --> 00:03:58,680
Knock him out with one punch,

92
00:03:59,039 --> 00:04:00,759
and see if this dream collapses.

93
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:04,759
Hey.

94
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,599
I just thought of something.

95
00:04:06,919 --> 00:04:07,759
Speak.

96
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,479
Is it possible

97
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:12,000
that you two drank too much last night

98
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:12,919
and were mistaken?

99
00:04:13,319 --> 00:04:15,680
We're actually in the real world right now,

100
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,800
not in a dream.

101
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:18,959
Which means Imperial Uncle Liu

102
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:21,000
just got hit for real.

103
00:04:23,319 --> 00:04:24,600
No way.

104
00:04:25,439 --> 00:04:26,240
Did that hurt?

105
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:29,920
No way.

106
00:04:31,519 --> 00:04:33,560
Then I'm done for, done for, done for.

107
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:34,839
How am I ever

108
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:36,600
going to become Empress?

109
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:37,240
I'm sorry.

110
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,480
Sorry, sorry.

111
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:39,279
Get up, get up.

112
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:55,759
Sigh.

113
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:58,600
I feel nothing at all. Totally blank.

114
00:04:58,839 --> 00:05:00,600
We must be in a dream, no doubt.

115
00:05:02,079 --> 00:05:03,759
But looking at Imperial Uncle Liu,

116
00:05:04,279 --> 00:05:05,560
he doesn't seem to be lying.

117
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:08,120
Because he really isn't lying.

118
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:11,800
You guys beat me way too hard!

119
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:12,519
Huh?

120
00:05:12,519 --> 00:05:14,600
You think you can just walk away?

121
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:18,759
We're in your dream.

122
00:05:18,759 --> 00:05:20,199
You swapped out our wine.

123
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,279
That's right.

124
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:25,000
I've served the Liu household faithfully for over twenty years.

125
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:26,040
Hmph!

126
00:05:26,519 --> 00:05:27,279
His Highness

127
00:05:27,279 --> 00:05:29,279
has never even scolded me once,

128
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:32,439
let alone beaten me.

129
00:05:33,199 --> 00:05:35,360
You all hit way too hard!

130
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:36,600
I'm not that forgiving.

131
00:05:36,879 --> 00:05:37,480
Ha!

132
00:05:37,839 --> 00:05:40,040
I'll make you pay in blood!

133
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:40,839
Fine!

134
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:41,759
Bring it on!

135
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:42,720
Who's afraid of who?

136
00:05:43,199 --> 00:05:43,600
Are you stupid?

137
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:43,839
This is his dream.

138
00:05:43,839 --> 00:05:44,519
You can't beat him.

139
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:45,480
Let's run!

140
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,279
Go, go, go!

141
00:05:46,759 --> 00:05:47,519
Ouch!

142
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:50,040
In my dream,

143
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:52,079
where can they possibly run to?

144
00:05:52,319 --> 00:05:53,120
No matter where they run,

145
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:55,279
I can find them.

146
00:06:02,279 --> 00:06:03,519
Huh?

147
00:06:04,199 --> 00:06:04,800
Hey.

148
00:06:04,959 --> 00:06:05,759
Where'd they go?

149
00:06:05,759 --> 00:06:06,920
Did we really run that fast?

150
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,199
This isn't quite what I expected.

151
00:06:08,199 --> 00:06:09,920
Why is it snowing?

152
00:06:11,959 --> 00:06:13,279
Hurry, hurry!

153
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:15,759
I'm telling you, come out yourselves!

154
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:19,360
I can see you!

155
00:06:22,079 --> 00:06:23,120
I'm warning you!

156
00:06:23,959 --> 00:06:25,480
I see everything!

157
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:28,519
I'm giving you a chance to come out on your own.

158
00:06:28,759 --> 00:06:29,519
Oh my.

159
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,959
Seems this dream isn't the steward's either.

160
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:41,800
Then whose could it be?

161
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,959
Whoever falls asleep first,

162
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:47,519
others enter their dream.

163
00:06:47,759 --> 00:06:48,959
First to fall asleep...

164
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:50,399
Isn't that the steward?

165
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:53,199
He poured us the Dream Wanderer Wine first.

166
00:06:53,399 --> 00:06:57,000
Then must've drunk it himself and gone to sleep.

167
00:06:57,079 --> 00:06:58,279
Otherwise how would he be here?

168
00:06:58,879 --> 00:07:00,920
The first to fall asleep...

169
00:07:03,439 --> 00:07:05,279
Wasn't the first to fall asleep Liu Heng?

170
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,519
Huh?

171
00:07:11,399 --> 00:07:12,279
Oh, right!

172
00:07:12,439 --> 00:07:13,439
It's all because of you!

173
00:07:15,199 --> 00:07:17,279
How was I supposed to know it'd turn out like this?

174
00:07:17,759 --> 00:07:18,920
Fine, fine, forget it.

175
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,240
If it's Liu Heng, this is actually easier.

176
00:07:20,879 --> 00:07:23,199
What Liu Heng wants most in his dream is to be Emperor.

177
00:07:23,319 --> 00:07:25,120
If we stop him from becoming Emperor,

178
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:27,040
the dream will naturally collapse.

179
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:27,519
But,

180
00:07:27,519 --> 00:07:29,319
Where do we find Liu Heng?

181
00:07:29,639 --> 00:07:30,439
Hmm.

182
00:07:31,279 --> 00:07:32,079
Liu Heng.

183
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,759
No need to find him.

184
00:07:34,959 --> 00:07:39,120
I have ways to make him come find us.

185
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:46,759
Imperial Uncle Liu declares his ascension to the throne of Daliang.

186
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:50,800
The coronation ceremony will be held in this city in three days.

187
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:53,279
Hereby proclaimed to all under heaven.

188
00:07:53,279 --> 00:07:53,920
Oh my!

189
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:55,959
Imperial Uncle Liu is becoming Emperor!

190
00:07:56,199 --> 00:07:57,680
Imperial Uncle Liu is becoming Emperor!

191
00:08:05,319 --> 00:08:07,800
If this is really inside Liu Heng's dream,

192
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:09,000
then where would he be?

193
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:10,319
He's probably in the palace right now,

194
00:08:10,319 --> 00:08:11,920
playing emperor to his heart's content.

195
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:13,959
Huh?

196
00:08:15,079 --> 00:08:17,920
The palace is a long way from here.

197
00:08:18,319 --> 00:08:19,120
So what do we do?

198
00:08:19,839 --> 00:08:21,240
We're in a dream, remember?

199
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:22,519
If he really wants to come,

200
00:08:22,519 --> 00:08:23,639
he can be here by tomorrow.

201
00:08:24,439 --> 00:08:26,079
His Majesty has arrived!

202
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:27,439
See?

203
00:08:27,439 --> 00:08:28,600
What did I tell you?

204
00:08:30,879 --> 00:08:31,680
Sigh.

205
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:38,279
His Majesty has arrived!

206
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:42,039
Oh?

207
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:44,200
If it isn't the Twenty-Eighth Prince.

208
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:45,600
A few days go by,

209
00:08:45,679 --> 00:08:47,120
and now you're the emperor?

210
00:08:47,759 --> 00:08:48,759
How about it?

211
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,720
I've already inherited the throne.

212
00:08:50,919 --> 00:08:51,720
Oh, really?

213
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:53,399
Who said you could inherit it?

214
00:08:54,279 --> 00:08:56,879
Last I checked, you weren't the Crown Prince.

215
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:58,000
Who gave you the right?

216
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:58,799
Hey,

217
00:09:00,399 --> 00:09:01,919
Eunuch Gao let me inherit it,

218
00:09:02,799 --> 00:09:03,759
along with his friends.

219
00:09:03,759 --> 00:09:04,519
Oh, please.

220
00:09:04,759 --> 00:09:06,799
Eunuch Gao doesn't get to decide that.

221
00:09:07,039 --> 00:09:07,679
What?

222
00:09:08,039 --> 00:09:09,919
I'm the special envoy seeking the throne's heir,

223
00:09:09,919 --> 00:09:12,480
and I've named Imperial Uncle Liu the new emperor.

224
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:14,120
He's being crowned in three days.

225
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:16,279
Hmph.

226
00:09:16,759 --> 00:09:18,600
That's exactly why I'm here today.

227
00:09:18,759 --> 00:09:19,679
Let me tell you,

228
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:20,960
Imperial Uncle Liu cannot be emperor.

229
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:21,759
I don't approve.

230
00:09:21,759 --> 00:09:22,200
Tsk.

231
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:24,000
Just look at Imperial Uncle Liu.

232
00:09:24,120 --> 00:09:25,120
Brother of the late emperor,

233
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,879
of pure royal bloodline,

234
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:27,799
with glorious military achievements,

235
00:09:27,799 --> 00:09:28,519
and skilled in governance.

236
00:09:28,519 --> 00:09:30,200
He's the perfect heir to the throne.

237
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,200
Now look at me.

238
00:09:31,279 --> 00:09:32,519
A special envoy appointed by the Crown Prince,

239
00:09:32,519 --> 00:09:33,519
holding the late emperor's jade pendant,

240
00:09:33,519 --> 00:09:34,799
with the power of final decision.

241
00:09:35,279 --> 00:09:36,600
Now look at yourself.

242
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:39,000
What have you got?

243
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:40,200
And you want to be emperor?

244
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,440
In your dreams.

245
00:09:42,039 --> 00:09:44,320
You illegitimate fake emperor,

246
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:46,679
how dare you stop our rightful emperor's coronation?

247
00:09:46,679 --> 00:09:47,240
Hey!

248
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:48,519
What nonsense are you spouting?

249
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:50,960
I don't care if he's my father's brother,

250
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:52,519
and I don't care if you're the Crown Prince's envoy.

251
00:09:52,879 --> 00:09:53,679
Let me tell you,

252
00:09:53,679 --> 00:09:55,320
I won't let Imperial Uncle Liu be emperor.

253
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,519
I'll have him arrested for sure.

254
00:09:58,519 --> 00:09:59,399
Fine then.

255
00:09:59,679 --> 00:10:00,840
Go ahead and arrest him.

256
00:10:01,039 --> 00:10:02,840
If you can catch him, more power to you.

257
00:10:03,039 --> 00:10:03,840
Your Majesty,

258
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:05,600
the traitor Imperial Uncle Liu has been captured.

259
00:10:08,639 --> 00:10:09,440
Excellent!

260
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:12,279
Bring him in for the three of you to see.

261
00:10:12,679 --> 00:10:14,799
Let's see who dares challenge Liu Heng for the throne now.

262
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:18,279
Imperial Uncle!

263
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:28,840
How did this happen?

264
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:30,919
I hid him so carefully.

265
00:10:30,919 --> 00:10:32,840
I knew he could cheat in his own dream,

266
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:34,480
but his obsession runs way too deep.

267
00:10:35,039 --> 00:10:36,159
How about it?

268
00:10:36,399 --> 00:10:38,279
No one's left to inherit the throne now, right?

269
00:10:38,639 --> 00:10:39,879
I am the emperor.

270
00:10:40,720 --> 00:10:41,360
Guards!

271
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:42,960
Take these three traitors

272
00:10:43,519 --> 00:10:44,320
and arrest them one by one.

273
00:10:44,919 --> 00:10:45,720
Wait a moment.

274
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:48,320
What is it?

275
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:49,320
I hereby declare

276
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:50,679
that I accept the throne.

277
00:10:50,799 --> 00:10:51,679
I'll be crowned at once.

278
00:10:51,879 --> 00:10:52,679
From now on,

279
00:10:52,879 --> 00:10:54,159
I am the emperor.

280
00:10:59,679 --> 00:11:01,240
Don't you love drawing comics most?

281
00:11:01,279 --> 00:11:02,519
And you don't want to be Emperor?

282
00:11:03,879 --> 00:11:05,759
I don't want to draw comics anymore.

283
00:11:05,759 --> 00:11:06,519
I just want to be Emperor.

284
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:07,519
How about that?

285
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:10,759
The Crown Prince is the sole legitimate heir.

286
00:11:11,240 --> 00:11:12,600
As long as he's willing to be Emperor,

287
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:14,240
no one can compete with him.

288
00:11:14,399 --> 00:11:15,759
No matter how badly you want the throne,

289
00:11:15,759 --> 00:11:17,759
you understand that, right?

290
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:18,919
I understand.

291
00:11:19,639 --> 00:11:20,919
I've always understood.

292
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:22,799
As long as the Crown Prince takes the throne,

293
00:11:23,399 --> 00:11:25,000
I have no shot at it.

294
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:27,039
But, dear brother,

295
00:11:27,279 --> 00:11:29,000
I thought you didn't want to be Emperor?

296
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:30,919
So don't fight me for the throne, okay?

297
00:11:31,759 --> 00:11:32,799
Not okay! Not okay!

298
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:33,799
Hey, you all!

299
00:11:34,679 --> 00:11:36,519
Kneel before the Emperor at once!

300
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:43,120
Long live the Emperor! Ten thousand years!

301
00:11:43,440 --> 00:11:44,679
You bunch of fools!

302
00:11:44,679 --> 00:11:45,720
Who are you calling Emperor?

303
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:46,799
I'm the real Emperor!

304
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:48,840
Oh my, my, my!

305
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:49,639
Who's this?

306
00:11:50,279 --> 00:11:53,519
Parading around in a dragon robe, swindling us?

307
00:11:53,759 --> 00:11:54,559
You there!

308
00:11:55,039 --> 00:11:56,960
Strip off his dragon robe!

309
00:11:57,360 --> 00:11:58,480
Put it on our Emperor!

310
00:11:58,679 --> 00:11:59,480
Who dares?

311
00:11:59,480 --> 00:12:00,000
Hey!

312
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:01,399
What are you doing?

313
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:03,480
Don't strip off my dragon robe!

314
00:12:04,279 --> 00:12:04,759
Ouyang Yan!

315
00:12:04,759 --> 00:12:05,159
You...

316
00:12:06,519 --> 00:12:07,600
How dare you!

317
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:08,919
You dare lay a hand on me?

318
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:11,200
I'll be back!

319
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:12,240
It's done.

320
00:12:15,039 --> 00:12:16,759
I really didn't expect

321
00:12:16,879 --> 00:12:19,000
Imperial Uncle Liu to be so devoted.

322
00:12:19,639 --> 00:12:21,399
Every man has a devoted side.

323
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:23,200
Sigh.

324
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:24,960
What man is like you,

325
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:26,960
devoted to a chicken?

326
00:12:27,519 --> 00:12:28,519
Oh, shut up!

327
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:29,519
Alright.

328
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:31,159
Stop bickering, you two.

329
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:32,759
What matters most now

330
00:12:32,919 --> 00:12:35,519
is hoping Imperial Uncle defeats Dubian Kingdom.

331
00:12:36,759 --> 00:12:39,440
But he can't even block one punch from me.

332
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:40,960
I'm starting to feel

333
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:42,159
this whole thing's looking shaky.

334
00:12:42,519 --> 00:12:44,879
Who in the world can block your Mountain-Splitting Punch?

335
00:12:46,799 --> 00:12:48,120
Good point.

336
00:12:48,799 --> 00:12:49,159
Hey!

337
00:12:49,799 --> 00:12:50,799
Stop pretending.

338
00:12:53,519 --> 00:12:54,679
Eunuch Gao has an accomplice.

339
00:12:55,759 --> 00:12:56,600
What did you say?

340
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:58,159
Do you all remember,

341
00:12:58,159 --> 00:12:59,960
when I asked Liu Heng who told him to take the throne,

342
00:13:00,120 --> 00:13:00,919
what he said?

343
00:13:01,320 --> 00:13:02,120
He said

344
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:05,039
Eunuch Gao told him to take the throne.

345
00:13:05,039 --> 00:13:05,840
No.

346
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:07,159
That was only the first half.

347
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:08,519
His exact words were:

348
00:13:08,720 --> 00:13:09,519
Hey,

349
00:13:09,759 --> 00:13:11,440
it was Eunuch Gao who told me to take the throne.

350
00:13:11,679 --> 00:13:12,480
Oh, right.

351
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:13,720
And his friends, too.

352
00:13:15,039 --> 00:13:16,399
Quite the impersonation.

353
00:13:17,519 --> 00:13:18,320
But

354
00:13:18,519 --> 00:13:19,879
words spoken in a dream

355
00:13:19,960 --> 00:13:21,000
can't be taken seriously, right?

356
00:13:21,399 --> 00:13:22,200
No.

357
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:23,840
Dreams come from the subconscious,

358
00:13:24,080 --> 00:13:26,240
and the subconscious cannot lie.

359
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:29,519
Liu Heng and Eunuch Gao were already colluding.

360
00:13:29,799 --> 00:13:31,000
At some point,

361
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:32,759
he must've accidentally seen Eunuch Gao's accomplice.

362
00:13:32,759 --> 00:13:34,120
But he wasn't sure who it was,

363
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:36,240
so it left an impression in his dreams.

364
00:13:36,960 --> 00:13:37,759
Crown Prince,

365
00:13:37,759 --> 00:13:39,240
better to believe it than dismiss it.

366
00:13:39,440 --> 00:13:42,519
Write to the palace and have them investigate the accomplice.

367
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:44,919
Alright.

368
00:13:44,919 --> 00:13:45,799
Got it.

369
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:50,399
I do a pretty good impression.

370
00:13:50,840 --> 00:13:51,639
Mm-hmm.

371
00:13:53,639 --> 00:13:54,440
Crown Prince.

372
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:56,240
I can imitate you too.

373
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:59,639
How can anyone be so handsome?

374
00:13:59,759 --> 00:14:00,679
Right, right!

375
00:14:01,039 --> 00:14:02,480
Not only is he handsome,

376
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:03,879
he's accomplished in his career,

377
00:14:04,080 --> 00:14:06,159
and incredibly talented too.

378
00:14:06,320 --> 00:14:08,080
Have you read that poetry book?

379
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:09,279
It's amazing!

380
00:14:09,519 --> 00:14:10,320
Sigh.

381
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:13,120
If only Blazing Sun Prince weren't married.

382
00:14:13,679 --> 00:14:15,240
Tomorrow he and Consort Zhen are competing in

383
00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:17,320
the "Daliang's Most Beautiful Couple" contest.

384
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:18,120
You don't stand a chance.

385
00:14:18,120 --> 00:14:18,919
Hey, hey, hey.

386
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:20,240
Did you hear that?

387
00:14:20,320 --> 00:14:22,360
Blazing Sun Prince sounds like quite a guy.

388
00:14:22,519 --> 00:14:24,480
Paintings for sale! Paintings for sale!

389
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:25,799
Painting seller!

390
00:14:26,279 --> 00:14:27,480
Get me a painting.

391
00:14:27,679 --> 00:14:28,360
Ah!

392
00:14:28,519 --> 00:14:29,759
You're in luck.

393
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:31,039
This one here

394
00:14:31,159 --> 00:14:34,320
is a limited edition by the official contest artist.

395
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:35,120
Take a look.

396
00:14:35,559 --> 00:14:38,039
See how exquisite the brushwork is?

397
00:14:38,519 --> 00:14:38,960
Wow.

398
00:14:39,200 --> 00:14:41,279
It really is beautifully painted.

399
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:42,639
Give me one too.

400
00:14:42,639 --> 00:14:42,799
Hey.

401
00:14:42,960 --> 00:14:43,679
Right away!

402
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:44,600
Forget hers.

403
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:45,759
What are you doing?

404
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:47,639
I'll use it as reference for my painting.

405
00:14:50,279 --> 00:14:51,240
Keep the change.

406
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:51,759
Hey.

407
00:14:51,879 --> 00:14:53,399
This isn't enough.

408
00:14:54,120 --> 00:14:55,000
Two taels per painting.

409
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:57,000
Two taels per painting!

410
00:14:57,120 --> 00:14:58,039
Forget it, never mind.

411
00:14:58,039 --> 00:14:58,360
Hey.

412
00:14:59,799 --> 00:15:00,600
Here.

413
00:15:03,200 --> 00:15:04,519
Paintings for sale!

414
00:15:05,559 --> 00:15:08,080
Home is wherever you are,

415
00:15:08,240 --> 00:15:10,200
without you, it's like a cliff's edge.

416
00:15:10,440 --> 00:15:10,759
Give it to me.

417
00:15:11,159 --> 00:15:13,600
This Blazing Sun Prince is quite the romantic.

418
00:15:14,320 --> 00:15:16,039
Step outside and you'd plunge to your death.

419
00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:18,320
What's with that attitude?

420
00:15:18,639 --> 00:15:20,159
Is that any way to talk?

421
00:15:20,240 --> 00:15:21,080
Got a problem with it?

422
00:15:21,080 --> 00:15:24,279
I wouldn't dare diss a man whose painting costs two taels.

423
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:26,399
Even the God of Wealth isn't that pricey.

424
00:15:26,399 --> 00:15:27,200
You don't get it.

425
00:15:28,240 --> 00:15:29,759
A man this perfect

426
00:15:31,639 --> 00:15:32,960
is absolutely perfect for me.

427
00:15:33,879 --> 00:15:36,519
There's no way such a perfect man exists.

428
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:39,320
Just because you can't, doesn't mean he doesn't exist.

429
00:15:40,080 --> 00:15:40,600
Fine.

430
00:15:40,600 --> 00:15:42,320
Even if we assume the impossible,

431
00:15:42,320 --> 00:15:43,799
even if such a perfect man existed,

432
00:15:43,799 --> 00:15:45,519
you'd never land him anyway.

433
00:15:45,919 --> 00:15:46,159
See that?

434
00:15:46,440 --> 00:15:46,759
Huh?

435
00:15:48,039 --> 00:15:50,279
Cooking for you, fussing over you,

436
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:52,320
making soup with her own hands.

437
00:15:52,320 --> 00:15:53,159
What he likes

438
00:15:53,440 --> 00:15:55,200
is this kind of virtuous, gentle woman.

439
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:56,399
Can you? Can you? Can you? No way you can.

440
00:15:57,840 --> 00:15:59,000
The way you're saying that

441
00:15:59,080 --> 00:16:00,679
sounds awfully jealous.

442
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:05,320
Am I jealous?

443
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:08,159
Why would I be jealous?

444
00:16:09,159 --> 00:16:09,679
Me?

445
00:16:10,200 --> 00:16:11,720
I'm not jealous at all.

446
00:16:11,720 --> 00:16:13,519
How am I worthy of such responsibility?

447
00:16:13,519 --> 00:16:15,279
Your Highness, no need to be modest.

448
00:16:15,440 --> 00:16:17,399
We've heard all about your deeds.

449
00:16:17,399 --> 00:16:19,240
A man like you not being my husband

450
00:16:19,240 --> 00:16:20,200
would truly be such a waste.

451
00:16:20,440 --> 00:16:20,879
Huh?

452
00:16:21,320 --> 00:16:21,639
Hey.

453
00:16:21,639 --> 00:16:25,159
She means you're perfect to be Emperor.

454
00:16:26,039 --> 00:16:27,480
I'm honored by the Envoy's regard.

455
00:16:27,480 --> 00:16:28,639
I dare not refuse.

456
00:16:28,960 --> 00:16:29,480
However, tomorrow

457
00:16:29,480 --> 00:16:31,600
is our Daliang's Most Beautiful Couple contest.

458
00:16:31,960 --> 00:16:34,279
I've spent nearly a year preparing for this.

459
00:16:35,240 --> 00:16:36,960
I beg you to grant me a few more days.

460
00:16:37,320 --> 00:16:38,679
Once the contest concludes,

461
00:16:38,679 --> 00:16:40,159
I'll head to the capital with you immediately.

462
00:16:40,159 --> 00:16:40,919
Wait, no.

463
00:16:40,919 --> 00:16:43,799
I keep hearing about this couple contest.

464
00:16:43,799 --> 00:16:44,759
What's it even for?

465
00:16:45,480 --> 00:16:46,879
My royal father started it.

466
00:16:47,440 --> 00:16:49,039
It used to be held only in the palace,

467
00:16:49,240 --> 00:16:52,080
to whip the philandering imperial uncles into shape.

468
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:53,720
Unexpectedly, it became a hit,

469
00:16:53,879 --> 00:16:55,200
so it spread among the common folk.

470
00:16:55,320 --> 00:16:57,120
You're about to become Emperor.

471
00:16:57,120 --> 00:16:58,440
Why bother with some contest?

472
00:16:58,440 --> 00:16:58,879
Exactly.

473
00:16:58,879 --> 00:16:59,919
There's no time to lose.

474
00:17:00,200 --> 00:17:01,919
Let's set off tomorrow.

475
00:17:02,279 --> 00:17:03,720
Princess Ouyang, you may not know,

476
00:17:03,799 --> 00:17:04,839
but for this contest,

477
00:17:04,839 --> 00:17:06,759
I've spent nearly a year promoting it.

478
00:17:07,279 --> 00:17:09,079
If I announce my withdrawal tomorrow,

479
00:17:09,079 --> 00:17:11,240
won't the people think I'm a man without honor?

480
00:17:13,119 --> 00:17:13,920
Your Highness,

481
00:17:14,519 --> 00:17:16,519
you are truly devoted to the people.

482
00:17:17,240 --> 00:17:19,599
I think he just cares about his own reputation.

483
00:17:20,759 --> 00:17:21,559
Uh...

484
00:17:21,559 --> 00:17:22,839
Well, in that case,

485
00:17:22,839 --> 00:17:23,440
we'll trouble you, Your Highness,

486
00:17:23,440 --> 00:17:26,400
to return with us to the capital right after the contest.

487
00:17:26,480 --> 00:17:27,400
Any delay,

488
00:17:27,839 --> 00:17:29,920
and bad things will happen.

489
00:17:35,160 --> 00:17:36,519
Thank you, Envoy, for accommodating.

490
00:17:36,839 --> 00:17:38,119
Once I ascend the throne,

491
00:17:38,119 --> 00:17:41,440
I'll devote myself fully to the people of the realm,

492
00:17:41,680 --> 00:17:43,640
giving my all until my last breath.

493
00:17:44,319 --> 00:17:45,400
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

494
00:17:45,480 --> 00:17:46,440
Once you're Emperor

495
00:17:46,920 --> 00:17:47,720
and married to me,

496
00:17:48,160 --> 00:17:49,759
devote yourself however you like.

497
00:17:50,720 --> 00:17:52,440
Princess Ouyang, what do you mean?

498
00:17:53,359 --> 00:17:53,880
Uh...

499
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:55,920
I don't understand your Daliang language well.

500
00:17:55,920 --> 00:17:57,480
That's about as far as I can go.

501
00:17:57,480 --> 00:17:58,720
Please don't put me on the spot.

502
00:17:59,079 --> 00:17:59,519
No, no, no.

503
00:18:00,599 --> 00:18:01,400
What I mean is,

504
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:03,640
what do you mean by "marry"?

505
00:18:05,599 --> 00:18:06,920
Marry means marry, doesn't it?

506
00:18:07,920 --> 00:18:09,720
Wedding bows, becoming your wife.

507
00:18:10,920 --> 00:18:12,319
I've made a vow with Consort Zhen,

508
00:18:12,519 --> 00:18:13,319
never to take a concubine.

509
00:18:13,319 --> 00:18:14,319
Who's asking to be your concubine?

510
00:18:14,319 --> 00:18:16,240
Just divorce her and marry me. Done.

511
00:18:17,720 --> 00:18:20,200
Why does becoming Emperor come with such conditions?

512
00:18:21,039 --> 00:18:22,519
What do you mean, conditions?

513
00:18:22,759 --> 00:18:24,039
This is clearly a perk.

514
00:18:25,200 --> 00:18:27,599
A beautiful young princess like me marrying you,

515
00:18:27,839 --> 00:18:28,920
what's there to complain about?

516
00:18:30,559 --> 00:18:32,640
Princess Ouyang is, of course, beautiful and brilliant.

517
00:18:33,160 --> 00:18:34,119
Naturally.

518
00:18:34,759 --> 00:18:37,440
But tomorrow I'm in the couple contest with Consort Zhen.

519
00:18:37,599 --> 00:18:39,200
How am I supposed to handle this?

520
00:18:39,400 --> 00:18:40,759
What era is this?

521
00:18:40,759 --> 00:18:41,920
It's just divorcing a wife.

522
00:18:41,920 --> 00:18:42,799
What's so hard about it?

523
00:18:44,559 --> 00:18:45,359
No.

524
00:18:46,240 --> 00:18:47,079
Absolutely not.

525
00:18:48,240 --> 00:18:50,039
You'd give up being Emperor just to avoid marrying me?

526
00:18:56,559 --> 00:18:57,319
Fine.

527
00:18:58,200 --> 00:18:59,400
If you won't marry me,

528
00:18:59,559 --> 00:19:00,799
you can't be Emperor.

529
00:19:01,519 --> 00:19:02,559
Weigh it yourself.

530
00:19:08,799 --> 00:19:09,440
Your Highness.

531
00:19:09,559 --> 00:19:10,480
Farewell, farewell.

532
00:19:11,799 --> 00:19:13,279
Fine, I won't marry her then.

533
00:19:16,839 --> 00:19:17,640
Your Highness!

534
00:19:18,400 --> 00:19:21,160
This is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity!

535
00:19:25,799 --> 00:19:27,240
About what happened earlier today,

536
00:19:27,599 --> 00:19:28,400
I'm terribly sorry.

537
00:19:28,559 --> 00:19:29,920
Please bear with us.

538
00:19:30,079 --> 00:19:30,920
Glad you know.

539
00:19:37,720 --> 00:19:38,359
Oh my.

540
00:19:39,079 --> 00:19:39,759
Oh my.

541
00:19:40,079 --> 00:19:41,680
This wine is so strong.

542
00:19:43,119 --> 00:19:44,920
Why am I suddenly so hot?

543
00:19:46,559 --> 00:19:48,319
Seems the Princess can't hold her liquor.

544
00:19:48,960 --> 00:19:49,640
Someone come here!

545
00:19:50,160 --> 00:19:51,200
Bring the Princess some tea.

546
00:19:51,200 --> 00:19:51,880
No need.

547
00:19:52,279 --> 00:19:53,680
In her current state,

548
00:19:53,759 --> 00:19:55,920
even drinking air would get her drunk.

549
00:19:58,319 --> 00:19:59,119
Ugh.

550
00:20:02,799 --> 00:20:03,440
Hey.

551
00:20:05,359 --> 00:20:06,039
Your Highness,

552
00:20:07,200 --> 00:20:08,759
Won't you even look at me?

553
00:20:13,920 --> 00:20:15,839
I'm a married man.

554
00:20:16,319 --> 00:20:17,880
Please conduct yourself properly, Princess.

555
00:20:18,599 --> 00:20:19,279
Hmph.

556
00:20:19,920 --> 00:20:21,599
That woman doesn't act like a wife at all.

557
00:20:21,920 --> 00:20:22,720
How dare you!

558
00:20:23,319 --> 00:20:24,559
What nonsense are you spouting?

559
00:20:26,480 --> 00:20:27,279
Your Highness,

560
00:20:27,880 --> 00:20:29,240
I truly don't understand.

561
00:20:29,519 --> 00:20:30,839
With your talent and strategy,

562
00:20:30,920 --> 00:20:31,720
why ruin your future

563
00:20:31,720 --> 00:20:33,480
over a woman like that?

564
00:20:34,759 --> 00:20:35,640
Stop it.

565
00:20:36,480 --> 00:20:37,920
Hey, hey, hey.

566
00:20:37,920 --> 00:20:39,680
Tell me what's wrong with that woman.

567
00:20:40,680 --> 00:20:43,720
Though His Highness dotes on Consort Zhen,

568
00:20:44,640 --> 00:20:45,880
she has never once

569
00:20:45,880 --> 00:20:47,319
fulfilled her duties as a consort.

570
00:20:48,279 --> 00:20:48,720
Hey.

571
00:20:48,759 --> 00:20:49,279
Your Highness,

572
00:20:50,000 --> 00:20:52,920
I heard you and your wife were quite the loving couple.

573
00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:54,799
That's only because His Highness spoils her.

574
00:20:56,200 --> 00:20:58,079
Since that woman married into the manor,

575
00:20:58,400 --> 00:21:00,079
she's never set foot outside the gates.

576
00:21:00,799 --> 00:21:02,680
She's sloppy and unkempt all day long.

577
00:21:03,720 --> 00:21:04,759
And lately,

578
00:21:05,519 --> 00:21:07,440
people have seen her sneaking around.

579
00:21:09,640 --> 00:21:11,000
The servants are all gossiping

580
00:21:12,640 --> 00:21:13,559
that she and some other man...

581
00:21:13,559 --> 00:21:13,920
They...

582
00:21:13,920 --> 00:21:14,440
Enough!

583
00:21:15,599 --> 00:21:17,000
I won't have you speak of her that way.

584
00:21:17,559 --> 00:21:18,319
Wow, Your Highness.

585
00:21:19,200 --> 00:21:22,000
You treat her so well and she still cheats?

586
00:21:23,000 --> 00:21:24,279
If you don't divorce a woman like that,

587
00:21:24,519 --> 00:21:25,720
what, are you keeping her for the holidays?

588
00:21:25,839 --> 00:21:27,319
Consort Zhen's family did me a great favor.

589
00:21:27,839 --> 00:21:28,920
This manor of mine

590
00:21:28,920 --> 00:21:31,599
was built thanks to her family's support.

591
00:21:31,680 --> 00:21:32,759
Oh.

592
00:21:33,720 --> 00:21:34,960
So you've been living off

593
00:21:35,519 --> 00:21:36,160
her family's money.

594
00:21:38,480 --> 00:21:39,200
A favor?

595
00:21:40,200 --> 00:21:43,559
A favor still doesn't justify cheating!

596
00:21:45,160 --> 00:21:45,920
Fine.

597
00:21:46,480 --> 00:21:49,000
Leave the divorce to me.

598
00:21:56,519 --> 00:21:57,319
Shh.

599
00:21:59,200 --> 00:22:01,599
Why are we meddling in someone's family affairs?

600
00:22:01,599 --> 00:22:02,799
What family affairs?

601
00:22:02,839 --> 00:22:04,039
This is my business now.

602
00:22:04,039 --> 00:22:04,960
Then I want to get involved even less.

603
00:22:05,160 --> 00:22:05,799
I'm leaving.

604
00:22:06,119 --> 00:22:07,160
Get back here.

605
00:22:07,440 --> 00:22:08,119
Catching cheaters!

606
00:22:08,319 --> 00:22:09,319
How fun is that?

607
00:22:09,599 --> 00:22:10,400
Exactly.

608
00:22:10,799 --> 00:22:12,359
You haven't even properly acknowledged me yet.

609
00:22:12,359 --> 00:22:13,039
Oh my goodness.

610
00:22:13,359 --> 00:22:14,799
A man's voice!

611
00:22:16,519 --> 00:22:17,480
Where are you going?

612
00:22:17,720 --> 00:22:18,880
We've gotta catch them in the act!

613
00:22:18,880 --> 00:22:19,319
Are you stupid?

614
00:22:19,319 --> 00:22:19,960
Based on just one sentence?

615
00:22:20,279 --> 00:22:21,880
What if she's talking to her wet nurse?

616
00:22:21,920 --> 00:22:22,720
Exactly.

617
00:22:22,880 --> 00:22:24,119
What are you trying to do?

618
00:22:24,720 --> 00:22:26,519
Why are you so obsessed with me?

619
00:22:28,599 --> 00:22:30,319
Whoa!

620
00:22:30,599 --> 00:22:31,160
Oh my god.

621
00:22:31,319 --> 00:22:32,160
Men's shoes!

622
00:22:32,279 --> 00:22:33,079
Whoa!

623
00:22:33,920 --> 00:22:35,720
Her lover must be in there.

624
00:22:36,160 --> 00:22:36,920
Hey, wait.

625
00:22:37,119 --> 00:22:38,319
Let's finish watching the show first.

626
00:22:38,599 --> 00:22:39,079
Huh?

627
00:22:39,079 --> 00:22:39,799
Oh, no, wait.

628
00:22:39,799 --> 00:22:40,960
Let's uncover the truth first.

629
00:22:40,960 --> 00:22:41,640
Keep watching.

630
00:22:43,319 --> 00:22:44,400
Oh my god.

631
00:22:45,160 --> 00:22:46,279
That's clearly a man.

632
00:22:47,119 --> 00:22:48,319
He's been cuckolded!

633
00:22:48,440 --> 00:22:50,119
They don't even close the door for this?

634
00:22:51,759 --> 00:22:53,319
I have to tell the Blazing Sun Prince the truth.

635
00:22:56,599 --> 00:22:57,279
Sigh.

636
00:22:57,519 --> 00:22:57,920
That's enough.

637
00:22:57,920 --> 00:22:58,759
Let's go back to sleep.

638
00:22:59,240 --> 00:23:00,119
Wait a minute.

639
00:23:00,720 --> 00:23:03,240
Why do I feel like that man in Consort Zhen's room

640
00:23:03,519 --> 00:23:04,839
is someone I've seen somewhere before?

641
00:23:04,839 --> 00:23:05,599
Forget it.

642
00:23:05,599 --> 00:23:06,799
You've never even left the palace.

643
00:23:06,799 --> 00:23:08,079
How could you know anyone from Blazing Sun City?

644
00:23:08,079 --> 00:23:09,559
What if I saw him here in the palace?

645
00:23:11,319 --> 00:23:12,559
You mean to say

646
00:23:13,000 --> 00:23:14,160
that Consort Zhen's lover

647
00:23:14,839 --> 00:23:16,319
might be a member of the royal family?

648
00:23:17,599 --> 00:23:18,559
Let me think.

649
00:23:22,160 --> 00:23:23,480
I've got it!

650
00:23:31,880 --> 00:23:32,559
Here you go.

651
00:23:32,680 --> 00:23:33,400
The evidence.

652
00:23:35,119 --> 00:23:36,039
Look at this.

653
00:23:36,039 --> 00:23:37,799
It even has Consort Zhen's embroidery.

654
00:23:37,799 --> 00:23:39,319
Clearly a gift for her lover.

655
00:23:44,319 --> 00:23:45,119
Hey.

656
00:23:45,400 --> 00:23:47,400
Don't be too sad.

657
00:23:49,440 --> 00:23:50,519
You were husband and wife.

658
00:23:51,160 --> 00:23:52,799
How could it end just like that?

659
00:23:53,599 --> 00:23:55,440
Out with the old, in with the new.

660
00:23:55,720 --> 00:23:56,640
Besides,

661
00:23:57,000 --> 00:23:59,799
isn't the new one already standing right in front of you?

662
00:24:01,200 --> 00:24:02,680
Princess Ouyang, you're so optimistic.

663
00:24:03,759 --> 00:24:04,559
Once you marry me,

664
00:24:04,559 --> 00:24:05,559
I'll be even more optimistic.

665
00:24:07,799 --> 00:24:09,039
You're so good to me.

666
00:24:14,000 --> 00:24:14,839
Look.

667
00:24:16,079 --> 00:24:16,839
This is...

668
00:24:16,839 --> 00:24:18,920
This copper coin had a flaw when it was minted.

669
00:24:19,160 --> 00:24:20,200
It came out heart-shaped.

670
00:24:20,240 --> 00:24:22,400
I found it interesting, so I kept it.

671
00:24:22,599 --> 00:24:25,119
It's the only one of its kind in this world.

672
00:24:25,319 --> 00:24:26,799
Now I'm giving it to you.

673
00:24:26,880 --> 00:24:28,200
This represents my...

674
00:24:29,160 --> 00:24:29,799
sincere heart for you.

675
00:24:30,640 --> 00:24:31,440
For me?

676
00:24:32,000 --> 00:24:32,799
Mm.

677
00:24:33,160 --> 00:24:37,079
So is this a token that you'll make me your empress?

678
00:24:37,720 --> 00:24:38,200
Yes.

679
00:24:38,599 --> 00:24:39,279
That's right.

680
00:24:39,880 --> 00:24:40,559
I...

681
00:24:41,880 --> 00:24:43,720
I realize I've already fallen in love with you.

682
00:24:45,880 --> 00:24:47,480
Who said anything about love?

683
00:24:47,759 --> 00:24:48,640
Get it straight.

684
00:24:48,640 --> 00:24:50,240
Me being empress is one thing,

685
00:24:50,240 --> 00:24:52,039
it has nothing to do with love.

686
00:24:52,720 --> 00:24:53,119
Ah.

687
00:24:53,119 --> 00:24:53,920
Also,

688
00:24:54,319 --> 00:24:55,640
after you marry me as your empress...

689
00:24:55,640 --> 00:24:56,440
Your Highness.

690
00:24:56,920 --> 00:24:57,720
Princess.

691
00:24:58,759 --> 00:24:59,559
What is it?

692
00:25:01,920 --> 00:25:02,759
He's here.

693
00:25:05,559 --> 00:25:06,519
Alright, you may go.

694
00:25:07,079 --> 00:25:07,880
Yes.

695
00:25:11,160 --> 00:25:11,880
Yan'er.

696
00:25:12,240 --> 00:25:12,920
It's getting late.

697
00:25:12,920 --> 00:25:14,200
Go back to your room and rest.

698
00:25:14,400 --> 00:25:16,160
I still have documents to review.

699
00:25:16,240 --> 00:25:17,759
After tomorrow's competition is over,

700
00:25:17,759 --> 00:25:18,880
write the divorce letter right away.

701
00:25:19,079 --> 00:25:19,759
Fine.

702
00:25:21,559 --> 00:25:22,119
Hey, hey, hey.

703
00:25:22,200 --> 00:25:23,880
I wasn't finished yet.

704
00:25:27,799 --> 00:25:29,519
We just locked eyes for eight whole seconds.

705
00:25:29,640 --> 00:25:30,319
Who are you?

706
00:25:30,319 --> 00:25:31,480
You read comics, don't you?

707
00:25:32,519 --> 00:25:33,599
You read "The Young Swordsman's Cliff Jump," right?

708
00:25:33,599 --> 00:25:34,279
Sorry.

709
00:25:34,279 --> 00:25:35,079
We got lost.

710
00:25:35,079 --> 00:25:35,759
We'll be going now.

711
00:25:36,160 --> 00:25:37,039
The outfit you're wearing,

712
00:25:37,200 --> 00:25:38,920
that's a character from "Snow Shadow Swordsman," isn't it?

713
00:25:39,680 --> 00:25:40,559
Mm, that's right.

714
00:25:40,559 --> 00:25:41,640
You read "Snow Shadow Swordsman" too?

715
00:25:41,640 --> 00:25:42,119
Wait.

716
00:25:42,440 --> 00:25:44,200
Why does your voice sound so much like a girl's?

717
00:25:44,920 --> 00:25:46,319
You're Consort Zhen, aren't you?

718
00:25:47,279 --> 00:25:48,640
Why are you dressed like a man in the middle of the night?

719
00:25:48,640 --> 00:25:50,240
Why did you barge into my room in the middle of the night?

720
00:25:50,240 --> 00:25:51,119
This is so awkward.

721
00:25:51,240 --> 00:25:52,039
Hey, wait.

722
00:25:52,240 --> 00:25:53,000
We just heard in your room...

723
00:25:53,000 --> 00:25:54,440
another person's voice. Who was it?

724
00:25:54,559 --> 00:25:56,440
Why are you so obsessed with me?

725
00:25:57,200 --> 00:25:58,599
She was reciting lines.

726
00:26:10,920 --> 00:26:12,599
Why are you two staring at each other again?

727
00:26:16,319 --> 00:26:17,559
I missed you so much!

728
00:26:18,640 --> 00:26:19,599
My little sweetheart.

729
00:26:20,599 --> 00:26:22,200
Why did you come here so late?

730
00:26:22,480 --> 00:26:23,599
Aren't you afraid of catching a cold?

731
00:26:25,759 --> 00:26:27,000
Don't talk to me.

732
00:26:30,000 --> 00:26:30,799
What's wrong?

733
00:26:33,160 --> 00:26:34,559
It's just that...

734
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:37,119
I was thinking about how tomorrow,

735
00:26:37,119 --> 00:26:39,200
you'll be showing off your affection for Consort Zhen in public.

736
00:26:39,880 --> 00:26:41,599
And it just breaks my heart.

737
00:26:43,319 --> 00:26:45,480
Why are you getting jealous over nothing?

738
00:26:45,519 --> 00:26:48,200
Don't you know who I really love?

739
00:26:48,880 --> 00:26:50,319
That's more like it.

740
00:26:55,640 --> 00:26:57,079
You go first.

741
00:26:58,920 --> 00:26:59,759
Be good.

742
00:27:05,319 --> 00:27:05,759
Oh.

743
00:27:06,000 --> 00:27:06,680
Your Highness.

744
00:27:07,680 --> 00:27:08,480
What a coincidence.

745
00:27:09,480 --> 00:27:11,920
My wife, what brings you here so late?

746
00:27:11,920 --> 00:27:13,039
Who are you calling wife?

747
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:14,799
I...

748
00:27:15,680 --> 00:27:16,599
I got lost.

749
00:27:16,799 --> 00:27:17,599
Oh.

750
00:27:17,920 --> 00:27:19,440
Then, my little baby,

751
00:27:19,839 --> 00:27:21,000
let me walk you back to your guest room.
